# COMMON PITFALLS

### Pitfall 1: Hardcoded Magic Numbers
**Wrong:**
```cpp
enemy.x += 100.0f; // What is 100?
```

**Right:**
```cpp
enemy.x += Config::Enemy::SPEED * deltaTime;
```

### Pitfall 2: Missing Error Checking
**Wrong:**
```cpp
Mix_Music* music = Mix_LoadMUS("music.ogg");
Mix_PlayMusic(music, -1);
```

**Right:**
```cpp
Mix_Music* music = Mix_LoadMUS("music.ogg");
if (!music) {
    SDL_Log("Failed to load music: %s", Mix_GetError());
    return false;
}
Mix_PlayMusic(music, -1);
```

### Pitfall 3: Not Validating Saves
**Wrong:**
```cpp
void loadSave(const GameState& state) {
    player.level = state.level; // No checks!
}
```

**Right:**
```cpp
void loadSave(const GameState& state) {
    if (state.level < 1 || state.level > 500) {
        SDL_Log("ERROR: Invalid level in save!");
        return false;
    }
    player.level = state.level;
}
```

### Pitfall 4: Memory Leaks
**Wrong:**
```cpp
SDL_Texture* tex = IMG_LoadTexture(renderer, "sprite.png");
// Never freed!
```

**Right:**
```cpp
SDL_Texture* tex = IMG_LoadTexture(renderer, "sprite.png");
// ... use texture
SDL_DestroyTexture(tex);
```

